data.description: Welcome to this truly spectacular, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, open concept residence in the highly desired Lago Mar West neighborhood of Miami, FL. Spanning over 2163 square feet of living space, this home embodies a perfect blend of style, charm, and functionality. Pride of ownership is evident with numerous recent upgrades throughout the home. Furthermore, the home boasts a brand new bathrooms and new kitchen, cementing the property's modern, up-to-date essence. The culinary enthusiast will certainly appreciate the completely updated kitchen. It features new cabinets and exquisite marble countertops. The home is located in A+ rating Schools, close to shopping centers, hospital and malls.
